The '''Forestry Practical Training Centre of Tabakoro''' (French: ''Centre de formation pratique forestier de Tabakoro'') is a practical [[forestry]] [[training school]] located in [[Tabakoro]], [[Sikasso Region]], [[Mali]], around {{convert|40|km|abbr=off}} east of the capitol, [[Bamako]]. The school's head office is located in Bamako.<ref>[http://www.infosysplus.org/db/db_index.php/door/upcome/dataset_id/3567/counter/1/main_unit/organisation/jump/choice/index.php Centre de Formation Pratique Forestier de Tabakoro]. The European Information System on Agricultural Research for Development (ARD). 2007-01-16</ref>
