48-0228-7|format=Paperback}} *{{cite book|editor-last=Rubin|editor-first=Arnold|title=Marks of civilization: Artistic transformations of the human body|date=1988|publisher=Museum of Cultural History, University of California, Los Angeles|location=Los Angeles|isbn=978-0-930741-12-9|format=Paperback}} {{Refend}}
